{"tid":2206141,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"五行會成員配偶 持未供斷房產","createTime":"2020-09-17T10:06:42.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-17T10:16:51.000Z","uid":25558,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"d8f3b08cdcacdba6a98d8ed786da6a90bedd7a2d","tid":2206141,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-17T10:06:42.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200917/SUDOMJUJNRHDPP65S4G56GFWII/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200917%2FSUDOMJUJNRHDPP65S4G56GFWII%2F&d=sV3HumZuViP2rFeoL7TNOHqjnVJZrvj6qhhAu%2BA3ahw%3D&h=617885c9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200917%2FSUDOMJUJNRHDPP65S4G56GFWII%2F&h=62938091\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200917/SUDOMJUJNRHDPP65S4G56GFWII/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n五行會成員配偶 持未供斷房產<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/u5rug3qs9jfd5zMszDJw9akMfZs=/720x462/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/67EABRUAIVAB7L5PWYT5GS5XZU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Fu5rug3qs9jfd5zMszDJw9akMfZs%3D%2F720x462%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F67EABRUAIVAB7L5PWYT5GS5XZU.jpg&h=cdebbf07&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■廖長江妻子王沛詩透過持股公司持有半山玫瑰別墅單位，至今年8月底仍未供斷。資料圖片<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】除官員外，行會各非官守成員亦是盛傳將被制裁的「大熱門」，查冊亦顯示，當中最少五人本身或配偶旗下物業仍有按揭未供完。「新界王」劉皇發的長子劉業強有份持股的「LWF Company Limited」持有屯門青山公路天佑居物業，自90年代以2,620萬元購入後曾獲多間銀行批出按揭，最新一份是在2014年轉按至中信銀行（國際），按揭文件未有顯示貸款金額。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n鄭若驊受制裁還清貸款<br />\n<br />\n至於張宇人的妻子蔡詠鈿及廖長江妻子王沛詩，分別透過持股公司持有藍田滙景花園及半山玫瑰別墅單位，兩物業分別在2010年及2012年獲花旗銀行及滙豐銀行批出按揭，至今年8月底仍未供斷。<br />\n<br />\n第一輪美國制裁名單早於8月7日公佈，。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n不幸「上榜」的鄭若驊事後雖揚言制裁是「徒勞無功」，鄧炳強更自稱「心情舒暢」，。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/3pNgXABVZtDkyVvMdmBh40MJJ1c=/3009x1700/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/I2JMZ5IN7VFDZC4JLSQPYHVBQY.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F3pNgXABVZtDkyVvMdmBh40MJJ1c%3D%2F3009x1700%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FI2JMZ5IN7VFDZC4JLSQPYHVBQY.gif&h=a82546a1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"fd3a538e41e2e06b850ea5d015ba4fdf27eb461a","tid":2206141,"uid":127575,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-17T10:07:20.000Z","msg":"有國家唔怕<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b5abec1b60655ad5d0212b31dcfa8eb9a7696501","tid":2206141,"uid":214173,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-17T10:10:20.000Z","msg":"全部轉晒去崑崙銀行繼續供樓<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/peanut.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c55b4b7f12b580c125a644ea709cbf7ab43b588f","tid":2206141,"uid":273218,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-17T10:16:51.000Z","msg":"估唔到美國制裁香港權貴<br />\n<br />\n會間接打冧香港樓價<br />\n<br />\n證明香港樓價只係靠少數人托住"}]}